38:22.778 --> 38:24.127
To umm...

38:26.086 --> 38:28.958
To a vacation in paradise,
I guess.

38:29.002 --> 38:30.830
[♪♪♪]

38:39.491 --> 38:40.535
Are you sure?

38:40.579 --> 38:41.623
Yeah.

38:51.981 --> 38:53.505
Well you were unfaithful
to your wife,

38:53.548 --> 38:55.594
is that why you broke up?

38:59.641 --> 39:02.340
Then what was it?

39:02.383 --> 39:04.559
I tried to give her
a good life

39:04.603 --> 39:08.389
and tried to make her happy,
but it wasn't enough.

39:08.433 --> 39:12.654
Happy on whose terms?
Your's or her's?

39:15.178 --> 39:18.094
I was as unfaithful
as they come.

39:18.138 --> 39:21.271
The way I see it, you do
what you can and feel alive.

39:24.100 --> 39:26.668
It's time I told you about the
years leading up to the war.

39:29.845 --> 39:32.065
