39:32.108 --> 39:35.329
You keep it pack as a reminder.

39:35.373 --> 39:37.549
You want to conquer
your weaknesses,

39:37.592 --> 39:39.507
keep them in plain sight.

39:41.422 --> 39:42.902
Speaking of which, how was--

39:44.817 --> 39:45.992
Who?

39:46.035 --> 39:49.212
You still have lipstick
on your neck.

39:49.256 --> 39:51.171
Don't you shower?
Jesus.

39:52.433 --> 39:55.784
So, Lucky was in jail.

39:55.828 --> 39:57.438
I wanted to get him
out of prison.

39:58.961 --> 40:01.399
How fast can we put together
an army of men?

40:01.442 --> 40:03.183
Fast?

40:03.226 --> 40:06.012
For what?

40:06.055 --> 40:07.666
