into them.

40:11.191 --> 40:12.192
Heil Hitler.

40:12.235 --> 40:13.498
Heil Hitler.

40:15.413 --> 40:17.545
MAN:
My [speaks foreign]

40:17.589 --> 40:20.113
We call upon our legislators
to evict [unclear].

40:20.156 --> 40:28.077
Jew is as alien in body,
mind and soul

40:28.121 --> 40:30.471
and it is more dangerous to us
than all the others

40:30.515 --> 40:33.735
by reason of its
parasitic nature.

40:33.779 --> 40:34.649
Heil Hitler.

40:34.693 --> 40:36.129
Heil Hitler.

40:41.787 --> 40:43.919
